item.title: Prayer bpn10254 in Māori
item.description: I runga i te Ingoa o Te Atua, te Namata, te Kaha Rawa. Waihoki, ko ngā ngākau pono kua peto ki te ahi o te wewete: kei whea te kirimōhinu o te mārama o Tōu Kanohi, e Te Tau o ngā ao? Ko ērā kua pātata ki a Koe kua whakarērēna ki te pōkerekere o te putu kau: Kei whea te pīataata o te ata o Tōu tūtatakitanga anō, e te Kōingo o ngā ao?
